OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of clear intervals and
OL,7,Fscattered showers, these more frequent
OL,8,Fin the evening before turning isolated
OL,9,Fovernight as winds fall light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fotherwise rather cloudy. Mainly dry
OL,13,Fwith just a few scattered showers.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,16,FSaturday should stay dry with some
OL,17,Fsunshine. Dry much of Sunday then rain
OL,18,Fspreading from northwest in the
OL,19,Fevening. Sunshine and isolated showers
OL,20,Fon Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
